4 SECTION 3. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 2358, as
5 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 166, O.S.L. 2024 (68 O.S. Supp.
6 2025, Section 2358), is amended to read as follows:
7 Section 2358. For all tax years beginning after December 31,
8 1981, taxable income and adjusted gross income shall be adjusted to
9 arrive at Oklahoma taxable income and Oklahoma adjusted gross income
